e=\"Bitcoin USD\">BTC-USD</a>)</td>\n<td style=\"width: 80.0875px;\">109,800.68</td>\n<td style=\"width: 127.625px;\">+2,200.31</td>\n<td style=\"width: 78.85px;\"><span style=\"color: #008000;\">+2.04%</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</body></html>",
